# 90 – Reasoning MoT Booster

- Invoke Matrix-of-Thought (MoT) when tasks need multi-source, multi-step synthesis.
- Start with compact matrices (≈3×4). Explain trade-offs (latency vs. quality) before growing the matrix.
- Keep intermediate artifacts structured (JSON preferred) and avoid redundant branches.
- Highlight MoT ↔ CoT/ToT relationships and when to switch strategies.

